{
  "name": "groundtruth-api",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "private": true,
  "description": "GroundTruth — orquestador NestJS: REST de comandos, webhook Helius, saga de certificación.",
  "scripts": {
    "build": "nest build",
    "start": "nest start",
    "dev": "nest start --watch",
    "start:prod": "node dist/main.js",
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit",
    "test": "vitest run",
    "test:watch": "vitest",
    "test:integration": "vitest run --config vitest.integration.config.ts"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@coral-xyz/anchor": "^0.32.1",
    "@irys/upload": "^0.0.15",
    "@irys/upload-solana": "^0.1.8",
    "@nestjs/common": "^11.0.0",
    "@nestjs/config": "^4.0.0",
    "@nestjs/core": "^11.0.0",
    "@nestjs/platform-express": "^11.0.0",
    "@solana/spl-token": "^0.4.15",
    "@solana/web3.js": "^1.98.4",
    "jose": "^5.9.0",
    "pdfkit": "^0.19.1",
    "pg": "^8.13.0",
    "reflect-metadata": "^0.2.2",
    "rxjs": "^7.8.1",
    "zod": "^3.23.8"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@nestjs/cli": "^11.0.0",
    "@types/express": "^5.0.0",
    "@types/node": "^22.0.0",
    "@types/pdfkit": "^0.17.6",
    "@types/pg": "^8.11.0",
    "typescript": "^5.6.0",
    "vitest": "^4.1.10"
  },
  "comment_decisiones": "Sin ORM: consultas SQL explicitas sobre pg (el esquema ya vive en supabase/migrations y es la fuente de verdad). Validacion con zod (mismo vocabulario que el frontend). Supabase JS no se usa aqui: el backend habla Postgres directo con el rol de servicio."
}
